hopobject.body: Withdraw cash costco pharmacy iwilei hours The Italian Treasury said on Tuesday it would offer up to 6billion euros of fixed-rate bonds (BTPs) and floating ratecertificates linking to the Euribor rate (CCTEU) at its regularmid-month auction on Oct. 11. * Italy will price on Wednesday its first-ever seven-yearbond, due in May 2021. Initial price thoughts on Tuesday pointedto a spread of 10-12 basis points over the March 2021 BTP bond.
